node.text:
This Saturday Kate is going live on Facebook to support the COVID-19 relief funds of @Musicares, @SweetReliefMusiciansFund and @Plus1org to help those in the live music industry who have lost work due to this pandemic. Human To Human will be 12 hours of live music noon-midnight EST

RSVP to watch here: https://smarturl.it/humantohumanFB
